com.enremmeta.rtb.constants

Interface RtbConstants

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Ad, BidPriceCalculator, Lot49Plugin, Tag
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdImpl, AdImplTest.Ad_1111_fake, AdITTest.Ad_181818_fake, AdTest.Ad_1234_segments, AdTest.Ad_181818_fake, BidCandidateManagerSpec.Ad_1001001_fake2, BidPriceCalculatorImpl, IntegralTest.Ad_1010_integral_fake, SharedSetUp.Ad_1001001_fake, SharedSetUp.Ad_1001001_mock, SharedSetUp.Tag_2002002_tagMarker_1001001_fake, TagImpl

    public interface RtbConstants
    Useful constants in RTB. This class only defines those constants that are found in documentation, whether OpenRTB or exchange-specific. Any constant that is defined by Lot49 project is in Lot49Constants.
    Author:
    Gregory Golberg (grisha@alum.mit.edu) Copyright Â© Enremmeta LLC 2014. All Rights Reserved.
    See Also:
    IABCategories, Lot49Constants
